
                                                        +-------+
                                                        |  .BT  |
                                                        +-------+

BOTTOM TITLE defines a running title  that will be printed at the
bottom of even- and odd-numbered pages.

     +-------+---------------------------------------------+
     |       |                                             |
     |  .BT  |    <<.U+>1<.U->|n>  /left/centre/right/               |<.NORMAL>
     |       |                                             |
     +-------+---------------------------------------------+

Equivalent to ".RT BOTTOM"; see .RT for details.

